variety of exciting vegetables used in every dish! Tonight's dinner is no exception with a rainbow of roasted veggies,
tossed together with leafy greens and topped by mildly spiced chicken. With a speedy prep time, you'll have this
warm and comforting meal gobbled down in no time at all.

